project_descr: Developing the Capacity of the Ministry of Economic Development to Monitor Progress towards Achievement of National Millenium Development Goals (MDG) Priorities.

outputs.output_descr: The main project output will be developed capacity in Ministry of Economic Development for coordination and monitoring of SPPRSD based on competent staff trained in data collection and analysis and able to assess progress against results-based indicators and to advise on results-oriented target setting.
